  "description": "The bounce engine with nowhere to be. Low gravity, very low bounce rate — the click cascade slows to a gentle nod rather than a driving pulse. Prism color dialed to the warm end of the spectrum, no drive, no fold. What funk sounds like on a Sunday afternoon when the errands are done and everyone is home.",
